{"tid":1686616,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"記者的時代革命 - 陳也","createTime":"2019-11-01T09:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T09:11:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"546b4a32493c7c8ee28a8da357455bfc86d7ba94","tid":1686616,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:10:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191101/20797534/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191101%2F20797534%2F&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvKRE6aJPUBN7WNjl4CDefRw%3D&h=847fcbad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191101%2F20797534%2F&h=60200c56\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191101/20797534/</a><br />\n<br />\n記者的時代革命 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191101/large/1572505549_5b24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191101%2Flarge%2F1572505549_5b24.jpg&h=f2a2639e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n96%新聞從業員反對政府發證，比例之高，文匯大公都有份反對囉，剩下4%，環球時報與新華社焗盲撐。<br />\n<br />\n記者奮勇作戰，外媒側目，有法國記者在抗爭現場採訪，發覺抗爭者主動提醒記者向哪個方向安全撤退，本地翻譯員覺得理所當然，法國記者含淚回應：我地那邊唔係咁㗎，示威者好憎記者㗎。各有前因，香港記者被黑警粗暴推跌、NOW車長被鎖帶返警署後下顎骨裂、學生記者被刻意招呼搜出所謂的尖銳武器只是一把切月餅餐刀，蘋果記者以至HKFP屢屢成為黑警欺凌的目標，立場新聞女記者在721元朗站被白衫惡棍毆打的直播畫面，更讓一位在港大念音樂系的內地生飽受驚嚇，震驚之餘尋求自保，出街時穿上反光衣扮記者自保。結果，被防暴警斷正。內地生庭上和盤托出「喬裝記者」時，只要是香港人，就能理解。記者以一件反光衣裝備，在黑警故意針對武力不斷升級的惡劣環境中反而遇強愈強，96%的新聞界，跟新聞系與學生會的年輕記者connect相同的歷史使命，擁抱資訊的時代革命，除了上帝，冇人可以DQ。 <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"882a483f4a00458f7ce027926bd9eb886380841f","tid":1686616,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T09:11:43.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，推post &amp; 借個靚位<br />\n<br />\n******眾籌*******<br />\n鐘庭耀教授為今次運動發起了超大型全港性民調，長期追蹤今次運動大事件的民意 (eg. 721, 831) &amp; 證明香港人未放棄，然後做份國際文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 話比全世界聽：5毛網軍不代表香港人<br />\n(<span style=\"color: red;\">眾籌到而家先40%</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 仲要大家支持)<br />\n<br />\n第二期民調結果POST <span style=\"color: red;\">(new)</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1686054</a><br />\n第一期民調結果POST<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1675545\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1675545</a><br />\n<br />\n民調眾籌LINK﹕<a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fproject%2Fstory%2F1209&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvKRE6aJPUBN7WNjl4CDefRw%3D&h=149b3bd7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/project/story/1209</a>"}]}